headline: AAR signs exclusive defense distribution agreement with AmSafe Bridport
summary: AAR CORP. (NYSE: AIR), a leading provider of aviation services to commercial and government operators, MROs, and OEMs, has signed a new multi-year defense distribution agreement with AmSafe Bridport, a TransDigm company.
